Class AbstractGuiFactory

java.lang.Object
factories.specification.AbstractGuiFactory
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable
Direct Known Subclasses:
GuiFactory
public abstract class AbstractGuiFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Closeable
This is the AbstractGuiFactory takes care of D.I in this project , from the GUI side(javafx) , providing us with every gui object we want
